flowchart LR
    Intent[Formal Intent]
    UCC[Capability Contracts / Telemetry]
    Scheduler[Multi-Currency Planner]
    Admission[Deterministic Admission Gate]
    Execution[Bounded Execution]
    State[Semantic State / Provenance Graph]
    Audit[Audit / Rollback / Explanation]

    Intent --> Scheduler
    UCC --> Scheduler
    Scheduler --> Admission
    Admission --> Execution
    Execution --> State
    State --> Audit
    Audit --> Scheduler
